# 🌊 Tracking Sea Level Rise in Mombasa

This interactive web project uses Leaflet.js to visualize the changes in mean sea level in **Mombasa, Kenya** across the years **1980**, **2000**, and **2020**. As users scroll through each section, the map updates dynamically to reflect the corresponding year's data.

## 🗺️ Features

- Story map interface with scroll-linked map updates
- GeoJSON-based time-series visualization
- Historical context for each year included in side panel
- Responsive layout using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript
